net.happybrackets.rendererengine

Annotation Type HBParam


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Inherited
 @Target(value=FIELD)
public @interface HBParam
    Annotation that defines a generic field (number or string) that will be exposed via OSC. OSC Port is defined by the oscPort field at a class that extends Renderer. It accepts fields with the following types: String, OSCMessage, float, int and boolean. The min/max is mandatory. If you do not want to specify a min/max, use HBParam.
